725600f-a.title: Queens: 72nd Street - 41st Avenue
725600f-a.text:
72nd Street, east side, at 41st Avenue, showing a group
of houses that were condemned for the cutting through of 441st
Avenue, seen in the foreground, toward 72nd Street. At this
point 41st Avenue passes over the tracks of the Long Island
Railroad.
P. L. Sperr  May 4, 1928
